data.description:
FSCJ Artist Series is a professional presenter of live performing arts specializing in touring Broadway, Concerts, Dance, Opera, Family, Comedy and Variety productions, and operates under the auspices of the Florida State College at Jacksonville Foundation. 

FSCJ Artist Series is a proud partner of Broadway Across America, a member of the Broadway League and a member of the Florida Professional Presenters Consortium.

From Blockbuster Broadway shows to cultural productions from around the world, the FSCJ Artist Series brings quality entertainment to individuals of all ages and backgrounds.

Touring productions presented by FSCJ Artist Series are held at Jacksonville Center for the Performing Arts and Florida State College at Jacksonville’s South Campus’ Nathan H. Wilson Center for the Arts.
